{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-00801/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-00801"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:08:01"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, pan, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman smiles as a man walks offscreen."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-00801","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-00801"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/canvas/1/b2d52d4d-26d1-4952-b77a-252d0c741e1b","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:20:22.994Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Henrietta’s lace collar here evokes the elaborate ruffs later spotted in the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW204866925 BCX0\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-04019.html\"><u>early modern portraits hanging behind Alma in the photoshoot</u></a>. Lace appears to be a favored material for Reynolds, incorporated as collars, hem details, and overlays throughout his designs.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:193.6313868613139,631.2481751824819,830.0474452554743,426.39416058394124"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/canvas/1/96360ff4-bd24-4eb8-a07b-56b59fe57976","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:20:34.508Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The costume design process was somewhat unusual in that it involved not only PTA and costume designer Mark Bridges but also Daniel Day-Lewis. On their influences and process, see “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW173276866 BCX0\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0B8Tf3Tvs1k\"><u>Academy Conversations: Phantom Thread</u></a>.”&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00801/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:10.182481751824817,45.733576642335834,232.45620437956205,142.43430656934297"}}}]}]}]}